Fossil calibrations

  • Crown Teleostei (Anaethalion zapporum†) 151.2 Ma
  • Elopiformes (Arratiaelops vectensis†) 126 Ma
  • Albuliformes + Anguilliformes (Baugeichthys caeruleus†) 129.4 Ma
  • Total group Angullidae (Anguilla ignota†) 47 Ma
  • Total group Serrivomer (Serrivomer sp.†) 12.62 Ma
  • Total group Echelus (Echelus branchialis†) 53.7 Ma
  • Total group Osteoglossidae (Paralycoptera wui†) 107 Ma
